name: Runic Magick
description:
1/1 Magic Runes in Elder Futhark Inscriptions
“Alu refers to the state between the world of the living and the dead, some kind of extasy or trance caused by an intoxicating drink. Thus the word might have been connected with death-cult, since the dead were often buried with a drinking vessel in order to enable them to participate in the eternal feast.”
